18-06-11|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2018/05/ryan-reynolds-michael-bay-netflix-six-underground-skydance-film-franchise-1202394010/|title=Netflix, Michael Bay, Ryan Reynolds & Skydance Set Action Franchise \u2018Six Underground\u2019|last=Jr|first=Mike Fleming|date=2018-05-22|work=Deadline|access-date=2018-06-11|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|[[David Ellison]], Dana Goldberg, [[Don Granger]] and Ian Bryce\n|[[Rhett Reese]] and [[Paul Wernick]]\n|[[Netflix]]\n|$150 million\n|{{N/A}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |TBA\n|''[[Robopocalypse]]''<ref name=\"D'Alessandro\"/>\n|[[Steven Spielberg]] \n|[[Drew Goddard]]\n| colspan=\"3\" |TBA\n|-\n| Untitled [[Poaching|elephant poaching]] documentary <ref name=\"RS\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/features/13-hours-can-michael-bay-pull-off-a-gritty-movie-about-benghazi-20160104?page=6|title=13 Hours': Can Michael Bay Pull Off a Gritty Movie About Benghazi?|author=Josh Eells|work=[[Rolling Stone]]|date=January 4, 2016|accessdate=March 10, 2016}}</ref>\n| TBA\n| TBA\n|Paramount Pictures\n| colspan=\"2\" | TBA\n|}\n\n==Frequent collaborators==\n\n===Actors/actresses===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:80%;\"\n|- style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"\n! Actors\n! ''[[Bad Boys (1995 film)|Bad Boys]]''<br />(1995)\n! ''[[The Rock (film)|The Rock]]''<br />(1996)\n! ''[[Armageddon (1998 film)|Armageddon]]''<br />(1998)\n! ''[[Pearl Harbor (film)|Pearl Harbor]]''<br />(2001)\n! ''[[Bad Boys II]]''<br />(2003)\n! ''[[The Island (2005 film)|The Island]]''<br />(2005)\n! ''[[Transformers (film)|Transformers]]''<br />(2007)\n! ''[[Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen|Transformers:<br />Revenge of the Fallen]]''<br />(2009)\n! ''[[Transformers: Dark of the Moon|Transformers:<br />Dark of the Moon]]''<br />(2011)\n! ''[[Pain & Gain]]''<br />(2013)\n! ''[[Transformers: Age of Extinction|Transformers:<br />Age of Extinction]]''<br />(2014)\n! ''[[13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers