istorical Perspective|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2RKTigrrP1cC&pg=PA13|year=1986|publisher=Atlantic |location=New Delhi}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Montgomery|first=Bernard Law|authorlink=Bernard Montgomery|title=A Concise History of Warfare|url=https://archive.org/details/concisehistoryof0000unse_r8u2|url-access=registration|year=1972|publisher=Collins}}\n* {{Cite book|title=Battles of the Honourable East India Company: Making of the Raj|isbn=978-81-313-0034-3|location=New Delhi|publisher=APH Publishing|year=2006|first=M.S|last=Naravane|url=https://books.google.com/?id=bxsa3jtHoCEC|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|first=Pramod K. |last=Nayar|title=English Writing and India, 1600\u20131920: Colonizing Aesthetics|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wpZ9AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA64|date= 2008|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-134-13150-1|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Nehru|first=Jawaharlal |authorlink=Jawaharlal Nehru|title=Discovery of India|url=https://archive.org/details/DiscoveryOfIndia|year=1946|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Delhi}}\n* {{cite book| title= Shivaji |page=21|isbn= 81-237-0647-2|publisher=National Book Trust |url= https://books.google.com/?id=_Rcfbh5e1_sC|first=Setumadhavarao S. |last=Pagdi |year= 1993|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal |first=M. N. |last=Pearson |title=Shivaji and the Decline of the Mughal Empire |journal=The Journal of Asian Studies |volume=35 |issue=2 |pages=221\u2013235 |date=February 1976 |jstor=2053980 |doi=10.2307/2053980|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|title=Encyclopaedic History of Indian Freedom Movement|first=Om|last=Prakash|publisher=Anmol Publications |year=2002|location=New Delhi|isbn=978-81-261-0938-8|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8ArbyWUf4j8C|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |title=The Indian Princes and their States |series=[[The New Cambridge History of India]] |first=Barbara N. |last=Ramusack |authorlink=Barbara Ramusack |publisher=Cambridge University Press |year=2004 |isbn=978-1-139-44908-3 |url=https://book