 Sarkar|first1=Sumit|last1=Sarkar|first2=Biswamoy|last2=Pati|editor=Biswamoy Pati|publisher=Popular Prakashan|year=2000|location=Mumbai|isbn=978-81-7154-658-9|url=https://books.google.com/?id=S2Yn4LlujqsC&dq=9788171546589}}\n* {{cite book|first=Gordon|last= Stewart|title=Marathas, marauders, and state formation in eighteenth-century India|publisher=Oxford University Press|date= 1994|ref=harv|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yBlKh1Pwof0C|isbn= 9780195633863}}\n* Suryanath U. Kamath (2001). A Concise History of Karnataka from pre-historic times to the present, Jupiter books, MCC, Bangalore (Reprinted 2002), OCLC: 7796041.\n\n{{refend}}\n\n{{MarathaEmpire}}\n{{Empires}}\n\n[[Category:Maratha Empire| ]]\n[[Category:1674 establishments in India]]\n[[Category:1818 disestablishments in India]]\n[[Category:Dynasties of India]]\n[[Category:Empires and kingdoms of India]]\n[[Category:Former confederations]]\n[[Category:Former countries in South Asia]]\n[[Category:Historical Hindu empires]]\n[[Category:Maharashtra]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1674]]\n", "name_user": "Blueflames228", "label": "safe", "comment": "grammer", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maratha_Empire"}
{"title_page": "Kolaambi", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian Malayalam-language drama film}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=June 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2019}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Kolaambi\n| image          = Kolaambi.jpeg\n| alt            = Kolambi\n| caption        = Official poster\n| director       = [[T. K. Rajeev Kumar]]\n| producer       = Roopesh Omana\n| writer         = T. K. Rajeev Kumar\n| starring       = [[Nithya Menon]]<br/>[[Dileesh Pothan]]<br/>[[Renji Panicker]]<br/>[[Sijoy Varghese]]\n| narrator       = \n| music          = [[Ramesh Narayan]]\n| cinematography = [[Ravi Varman]]\n| editing        = \n| studio         = Nirmalyam Cinema\n| distributor    = Pallavi Release\n| released       =\n| runtime        = \n| country        = India\n| language       = Malayalam\n| budget         = <!--Do not add without providing a source that has a reputation for fact checking and editorial oversight.-->\n| gross          = <!--Do not add without providing a source that has a reputation for fact checking and editorial oversight.-->\n}}\n\n'''''Kolaambi ''''' ({{translation|Loudspeaker}}) is an upcoming Indian [[Malayalam]]-language [[Drama (film and television)|drama film]] written and directed by [[T. K. Rajeev Kumar]], starring [[Nithya Menen]], [[Renji Panicker]], [[Sijoy Varghese]] and [[Dileesh Pothan]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsbugz.com/kolambi-malayalam-movie/|title=Kolambi Malayalam Movie (2019) {{!}} Cast {{!}} Teaser {{!}} Trailer {{!}} Release Date|last=Agatheeswaran|date=2019-06-04|website=News Bugz|language=en-US|access-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620085301/https://www.newsbugz.com/kolambi-malayalam-movie/|archive-date=20 June 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The film is produced by Roopesh Omana under the production house Nirmalyam Cinema. [[Resul Pookutty]] handles the sound recording, while music is composed by [[Ramesh Narayan]] and cinematography is done by [[Ravi Varman]].<ref>{{cite web | last=Native | first=Digital | title=Nithya Menen to team up with Rajeev Kumar for 'Kolambi' | website=The News Minute | date=26 November 2018 | url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/nithya-menen-team-rajeev-kumar-kolambi-92259 | access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/kolambi-trailer-magnificient-visuals-combined-with-effective-storytelling/articleshow/69650631.cms|title='Kolambi' trailer: Magnificient{{sic|hide=y}} visuals combined with effective storytelling|date=4 June 2019|newspaper=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610043718/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/kolambi-trailer-magnificient-visuals-combined-with-effective-storytelling/articleshow/69650631.cms|archive-date=10 June 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Production design is done by [[Sabu Cyril]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://malayalam.indianexpress.com/entertainment/kolambi-movie-trailer-released-nithya-menon-and-ranji-panicker-shines-264189/|title=\u0d09\u0d1a\u0d4d\u0d1a\u0d2d\u0d3e\u0d37\u0d3f\u0d23\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d33\u0d41\u0d1f\u0d46 \u0d15\u0d3e\u0d32\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d47\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d4d \u0d28\u0d3f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d2f \u0d2e\u0d47\u0d28\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d31\u0d46 \u2018\u0d15\u0d4b\u0d33\u0d3e\u0d2e\u0d4d\u0d2a\u0d3f\u2019; \u0d1e\u0d46\u0d1f\u0d4d\u0d1f\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d41\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d28 \u0d17\u0d46\u0d31\u0d4d\u0d31\u0d2a\u0d4d\u0d2a\u0d3f\u0d32\u0d4d\u200d \u0d30\u0d1e\u0d4d\u0d1c\u0d3f \u0d2a\u0d23\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d30\u0d4d\u200d|date=2019-06-03|website=Indian Express Malayalam|language=ml|access-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620091857/https://malayalam.indianexpress.com/entertainment/kolambi-movie-trailer-released-nithya-menon-and-ranji-panicker-shines-264189/|archive-date=20 June 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n''Kolaambi'' was selected in Indian Panorama, at 50th [[International Film Festival of India|\nInternational Film Festival of India (IFFI)]], Goa, held from 20 November to 28. It was premiered at the festival.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mathrubhumi.com/movies-music/news/iffi-goa-2019-uyare-jallikkattu-kolambi-selected-to-indian-panorama-1.4176666|title=50-\u0d3e\u0d2e\u0d24\u0d4d \u0d17\u0d4b\u0d35 \u0d1a\u0d32\u0d1a\u0d4d\u0d1a\u0d3f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d2e\u0d47\u0d33\u0d2f\u0d3f\u0d32\u0d47\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d4d \u0d09\u0d2f\u0d30\u0d46\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d15\u0d4b\u0d33\u0d3e\u0d2e\u0d4d\u0d2a\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d1c\u0d32\u0d4d\u0d32\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d46\u0d1f\u0d4d\u0d1f\u0d41\u0d02|website=Mathrubhumi|language=ml|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.manoramaonline.com/news/latest-news/2019/10/06/iffi-2019-three-malayalam-movies-selected-to-indian-panorama.html|title=\u0d09\u0d2f\u0d30\u0d46\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d1c\u0d32\u0d4d\u0d32\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d46\u0d1f\u0d4d\u0d1f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d15\u0d4b\u0d33\u0d3e\u0d2e\u0d4d\u0d2a\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d30\u0d3e\u0d1c\u0d4d\u0d2f\u0d3e\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d30 \u0d2e\u0d47\u0d33\u0d2f\u0d3f\u0d7d; \u0d07\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d35\u0d23 \u0d38\u0d3f\u0d28\u0d3f\u0d2e \u2018\u0d15\u0d47\u0d7e\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d3e\u0d02\u2019|website=www.manoramaonline.com|language=ml|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://english.manoramaonline.com/entertainment/entertainment-news/2019/10/06/malayalam-movies-iffi-priyadarshan-goa.html|title='Jallikattu', 'Uyare' and 'Kolambi' to be screened at 50th IFFI in Goa|website=OnManorama}}</ref>\n\n== Cast ==\n<!--As this film has not yet been released, additions to this section must be sourced, per WP:CRYSTAL.-->\n* [[Nithya Menon]] as Arundhati\n* [[Renji Panicker]]\n* [[Dileesh Pothan]] as Bank Manager\n* [[Sijoy Varghese]] as Sanjay Tharakan\n* [[Rohini (actress)|Rohini]] as Sundarambal\n* [[Aristo Suresh]] as Aampli Naanu\n* [[Siddharth Menon]] as Solomon\n* [[Baiju Santhosh]] as Moulavi\n* [[Vijay Yesudas]]\n* [[Manju Pillai]] as Lawyer\n* Suresh Kumar as Varghese\n* [[P. Balachandran]] as Kamal Pasha\n* [[Pauly Valsan]] as Alphonse\n* [[Jayakrishnan]]\n* [[Asha Aravind]]\n\n==Production==\nKolaambi marks the 25th film and directorial come back of director T. K Rajeev Kumar after  nearly 6 years.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.manoramaonline.com/movies/movie-news/2018/10/17/t-k-rajeev-kumar-come-back-with-new-movie-nithya-menon.html|title=\u0d30\u0d4b\u0d17\u0d19\u0d4d\u0d19\u0d33\u0d4b\u0d1f\u0d4d \u0d2a\u0d3e\u0d2f\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d2a\u0d4d\u0d2a\u0d4d; \u0d2a\u0d41\u0d24\u0d3f\u0d2f \u0d1a\u0d3f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d35\u0d41\u0d2e\u0d3e\u0d2f\u0d3f \u0d1f\u0d3f.\u0d15\u0d46. \u0d30\u0d3e\u0d1c\u0d40\u0d35\u0d4d \u0d15\u0d41\u0d2e\u0d3e\u0d30\u0d4d\u200d|website=ManoramaOnline|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref> [[Resul Pookutty]] was roped in to do sound recording. [[Ravi Varman]] was signed as the cinematographer and [[Sabu Cyril]] as the production designer.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cms.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/malayalam/2018/oct/24/nithya-menen-in-t-k-rajeev-kumars-next-kolambi-1889096.html|title=Nithya Menen in T K Rajeev Kumar\u2019s next, Kolambi|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref> Nithya Menen was roped in to do the role of biennale artist, marks her second collaboration with [[T. K. Rajeev Kumar]] after ''[[Thalsamayam Oru Penkutty]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/nithya-menen-team-rajeev-kumar-kolambi-92259?amp|title=Nithya Menen to team up with Rajeev Kumar for 'Kolambi'|last=|first=|date=|website=www.thenewsminute.com|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref>\n\nPrincipal photography of the film was commenced at [[Thiruvananthapuram|Thiruvanathapuram]] on 18 October 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/nithya-menens-next-malayalam-film-is-kolambi/articleshow/66347294.cms|title=Nithya Menen's next Malayalam film is Kolambi - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://m.cinemaexpress.com/article/nithya-menen-in-tk-rajeev-kumars-next-kolambi/8447/amp|title=Nithya Menen in\u00a0TK Rajeev Kumar\u2019s next, Kolambi {{!}} cinemaexpress|website=m.cinemaexpress.com|access-date=2019-10-06}}</ref>\n\n== Marketing ==\nThe trailer of the film was released on 3 June 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/malayalam/kolambi-trailer-nithya-menon-promises-a-feel-good-nostalgic-film-5763079/|title=Kolambi trailer: Nithya Menon promises a feel-good nostalgic film|date=2019-06-03|website=The Indian Express|language=en-IN|access-date=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621070317/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/malayalam/kolambi-trailer-nithya-menon-promises-a-feel-good-nostalgic-film-5763079/|archive-date=21 June 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nowrunning.com/movie/23264/malayalam/kolambi/|title=Kolambi (2019) \u2013 Kolambi Malayalam Movie|website=NOWRUNNING|language=en|access-date=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621070319/https://www.nowrunning.com/movie/23264/malayalam/kolambi/|archive-date=21 June 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The animation teaser of the film was released on 24 July 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/nithya-menen-starrer-kolambi-releases-its-animation-teaser-watch-video-463537|title=Nithya Menen starrer Kolambi releases its animation teaser; Watch Video|website=PINKVILLA|language=en|access-date=2019-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724180634/http://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/nithya-menen-starrer-kolambi-releases-its-animation-teaser-watch-video-463537|archive-date=24 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bo